    <item>
      <title>經典外型設計，純電豪華越野車， Mercedes Benz G580 with EQ Technology AMG Line</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/05/12/2025-mercedes-benz-g580-eq/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=2025-mercedes-benz-g580-eq</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/05/12/2025-mercedes-benz-g580-eq/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>arthur</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 May 2025 09:10:27 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>汽車科技</category>
      <category>4WD</category>
      <category>benz</category>
      <category>G-Class</category>
      <category>g580</category>
      <category>JEEP</category>
      <category>Mercedes-Benz</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1306762</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;平治最新電動豪華越野車 G580 with EQ Technology AMG Line，現已於香港正式接受預訂。這款全新 G-Class 不但保留經典外型與招牌設計，更配備四台獨立馬達及高壓鋰離子電池，提供 491 公里（WLTP）續航與 587 匹馬力輸出，並引入 G-TURN、G-STEERING 等先進功能，進一步提升越野表現。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110155_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110155_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110155_-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;全新電動 G-Class 在底盤安裝了 116 kWh 容量鋰電池，強化車身低重心，並支援最大 1,164 牛頓米扭力。其梯形車架配合創新驅動系統，令車輛具備傳統 G-Class 的堅固風格，同時引入多項全新越野技術，提升駕駛靈活性與安全控制力。全新電動 G-Class 具有創新的驅動概念，帶來全新獨特的越野駕駛功能：G-TURN、G-STEERING 和智能越野爬升功能。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110715-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110715-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110715-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110325-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110325-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110325-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110210-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110210-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110210-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;外觀方面，車身保持經典方正線條，標誌性後尾備胎設計依然保留。AMG Line 套件進一步強化動感格調，配備延伸輪拱、銀色鍍鉻保險桿與鋁質側裙，展現高性能氣息。後尾備胎上半部採黑色處理，下半部則與車身同色，強調獨特造型。客戶亦可透過 MANUFAKTUR 客製化服務，選擇個人喜好的配色與物料，打造專屬座駕，反映個性品味。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306767" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110743-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110743-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110743-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110444-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110444-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110444-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110259-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110259-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110259-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1306771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110232-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110232-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_20250512_110232-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;欲查詢預訂詳情，可親臨柴灣嘉業街 60 號或紅磡寶來街 50 號品牌中心。根據梅賽德斯—奔馳香港有限公司資料，該公司自 2006 年起負責 Mercedes-Benz、Mercedes-EQ、Mercedes-AMG 及 Mercedes-Maybach 等品牌在香港及澳門的汽車進口業務。自 2013 年起更完全脫離中國業務運作，獨立負責本地市場發展。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mercedes Benz G580 with EQ Technology 規格表:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;馬力: 587hp AWD&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;扭力: 1,164Nm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;加速: 0-100Km/h 4.7 秒&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;電池容量: 116kWh&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;續航力: 491 公里&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;尺寸: 4863mm x 2187mm x 1983mm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;售價: $2,380,000 起&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;來源:新聞稿&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
</description>
